inputs.name: StepSettings
inputs.value:
{"version":"KqlItem/1.0","query":"InvClientDefenderAvV2_CL 
| summarize CollectionTime = arg_max(CollectionTime,*) by Computer

          (AMRunningMode != "EDR Block Mode") and (AMRunningMode != "Passive Mode") and 
          (AntispywareEnabled == true) and 
          ( (TamperProtectionSource == "ATP") or (TamperProtectionSource == "Intune") ) and (IsTamperProtected == true)

| summarize total = count()","size":0,"title":"COMPLIANT DEFENDER AV | CLIENTS | COUNT ","queryType":0,"resourceType":"microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces","crossComponentResources":["/subscriptions/fce4f282-fcc6-43fb-94d8-bf1701b862c3/resourceGroups/rg-logworkspaces-client-demo6470D-t/providers/Microsoft.OperationalInsights/workspaces/log-management-client-demo6470D-t"],"visualization":"tiles","gridSettings":{"rowLimit":10000},"tileSettings":{"titleContent":{"columnMatch":"total","formatter":12,"formatOptions":{"min":0,"palette":"green"}},"showBorder":true,"size":"auto"}}
